Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.22,0:01:36.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小心點兒啊 仁碳
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.24,0:01:39.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宿海！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.27,0:01:40.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒 沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.87,0:01:47.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪集…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.09,0:01:51.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那件…連衣裙
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.95,0:01:54.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和芽間穿的那件很像
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.97,0:01:59.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎…怎麼穿成那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.44,0:02:04.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃…沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.97,0:02:08.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看起來…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.49,0:02:09.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像沒事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.99,0:02:16.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.01,0:02:18.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我看清楚啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.26,0:02:19.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 雪集！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.93,0:02:22.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.88,0:02:23.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要插手
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.57,0:02:25.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但 但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.86,0:02:26.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是個機會啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.33,0:02:28.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果這次錯過了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.05,0:02:30.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯定…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.23,0:02:31.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就再也沒…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.32,0:02:32.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鶴見子…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.85,0:02:37.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.43,0:02:39.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看起來像芽間嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.01,0:02:42.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能看見芽間吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.60,0:02:45.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 看上去像芽間嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.94,0:02:46.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪集…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.31,0:02:47.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底像不像！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.89,0:02:50.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我的錯啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.18,0:02:53.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那天 芽間會死掉…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.61,0:02:55.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我的錯啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.85,0:02:56.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…說什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.33,0:02:58.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會是你的錯啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.96,0:02:59.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倒不如說是我的…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.63,0:03:01.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都說是我的錯了！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.01,0:03:04.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要是沒對芽間說那樣的話
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.40,0:03:05.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芽間就不會死了…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.52,0:03:08.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我害死芽間的啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.16,0:03:14.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芽間要是出現的話
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.84,0:03:16.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該出現在我的面前
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.35,0:03:17.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,變鬼也好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.38,0:03:18.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,詛咒也好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.09,0:03:20.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也該…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.29,0:03:21.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也該在我的面前！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.35,0:03:27.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…但是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.81,0:03:29.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芽間沒有出現
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.49,0:03:32.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有出現在我面前
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.52,0:03:35.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪集…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.48,0:03:38.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以說 芽間已經不在了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.61,0:03:41.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再也…不在這個世上了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.76,0:03:46.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.19,0:03:58.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芽間說「我就在這裡」…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.42,0:04:00.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.11,0:04:02.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還在說那種話…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.06,0:04:06.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芽…芽間讓我對你說
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.49,0:04:09.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,, 「髮夾 謝謝」
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.96,0:04:12.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,, 「對不起」
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.76,0:04:17.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.74,0:04:21.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我雖然不太清楚 就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.43,0:04:23.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…雪集？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.29,0:04:33.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,滿意了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.55,0:04:39.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就這樣放他走好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.97,0:04:44.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好癢…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.94,0:04:48.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我先走了 辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.57,0:04:50.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你已經知道了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.21,0:04:52.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一早就
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.55,0:04:56.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是…多少有些懷疑
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.84,0:05:01.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為從很早開始 我就陪他一起放學回家了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.01,0:05:06.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裝作要給神秘女朋友送禮物的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.38,0:05:09.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女裝的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.46,0:05:13.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白色 帶絲帶的連衣裙
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.06,0:05:17.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那樣就好了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.41,0:05:19.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.79,0:05:21.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,膿要放出來才好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.11,0:05:22.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.74,0:05:25.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙已經爛到芯裡去了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.05,0:05:27.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把膿全部放出來的話
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.97,0:05:30.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能就剩不下什麼了…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.29,0:05:33.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.17,0:05:45.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「髮夾 謝謝 對不起」
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.44,0:05:56.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芽間
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.22,0:05:59.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 仁碳
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.57,0:06:01.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁碳！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.87,0:06:02.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.19,0:06:04.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等啊 芽間
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.65,0:06:05.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.34,0:06:07.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能等等啊 仁碳要走掉…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.16,0:06:08.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走掉就走掉吧 那種傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.70,0:06:17.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芽間才不是什麼醜八怪
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.38,0:06:18.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芽間是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.72,0:06:20.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.57,0:06:25.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得這個很適合 芽間你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.78,0:06:29.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很適合 我最喜歡的芽間！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.10,0:06:40.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.82,0:06:42.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁 仁碳走掉了 所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.46,0:06:46.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芽間必須去追仁碳 所以
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.62,0:06:47.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,待會再見
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.61,0:06:50.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芽間…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.72,0:07:33.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戴著眼鏡好像差點兒呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.04,0:07:39.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…看不見了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.72,0:07:45.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 芽…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.21,0:07:52.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芽…間…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.07,0:07:57.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.68,0:08:00.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想吃點兒什麼嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.66,0:08:03.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯我想想…阿健拉麵
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.28,0:08:05.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,家裡沒有呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.24,0:08:08.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再說了最近都沒看到那個
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.24,0:08:08.45,explain,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a5}註：阿健拉麵已停產
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.53,0:08:12.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會吧 那怎麼辦呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.75,0:08:15.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去買回來
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.64,0:08:18.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了 不用特意跑一趟
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.14,0:08:19.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,家裡有的東西就行…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.66,0:08:22.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁碳？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.53,0:08:24.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芽間死了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.07,0:08:27.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卻又在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.32,0:08:30.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是在雪集那裡 而是在我這
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.15,0:08:34.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幽靈也好 妄想也好 怎麼都無所謂
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.11,0:08:36.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…我這樣想
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.91,0:08:38.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.68,0:08:41.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我其實只是不去想而已
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.98,0:08:46.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和大家在一起 很快樂
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.07,0:08:49.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和仁碳在一起 很快樂
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.21,0:08:54.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 即使不認真去想也沒問題
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.72,0:08:56.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…我總這麼覺得
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.99,0:08:59.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芽間她
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.14,0:09:02.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼會在這裡呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.66,0:09:06.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太受歡迎啦 你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.64,0:09:33.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為沒有阿健拉麵
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.29,0:09:34.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就買了別的代替
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.41,0:09:36.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,代替…這麼多？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.25,0:09:39.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.63,0:09:46.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啦 快點兒坐…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.67,0:09:47.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁碳
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.51,0:09:48.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有話要說
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.47,0:09:51.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有話要說是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.04,0:09:53.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過你看
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.17,0:09:54.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「喀嚓喀嚓」冰棍要 要化了…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.70,0:09:57.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請你幫我 實現我的願望
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.08,0:10:01.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事到如今你在說些什麼呀
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.92,0:10:04.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我正按自己的做法來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.34,0:10:07.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…各種做法
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.99,0:10:12.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然不像雪集那麼怨念…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.46,0:10:14.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.29,0:10:16.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也有自己的…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.71,0:10:24.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也 有很多自己的事情要忙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.85,0:10:27.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒閒工夫一直關心你的事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.54,0:10:29.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁碳…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.18,0:10:30.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回來啦～
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.15,0:10:34.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉 今天也好累…哦！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.05,0:10:36.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些是怎麼回事 要開party嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.89,0:10:39.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊～ 「喀嚓喀嚓」好可愛～
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.83,0:10:42.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以吃嗎 …啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.61,0:10:45.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可愛…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.22,0:10:47.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.58,0:10:50.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說什麼「自己的事情」
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.63,0:10:53.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有什麼好忙的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.61,0:10:56.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃飯 上網 睡覺…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.76,0:10:59.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遊戲 睡覺 吃飯 …
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.75,0:11:02.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是在不斷重複吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.05,0:11:03.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我卻…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.91,0:11:10.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我卻…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.06,0:11:15.02,title_no,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(623,607)}第五集
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.06,0:11:15.02,title_text,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(781,684)}隧道
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.10,0:11:17.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.00,0:11:20.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回去的時候就直接坐電車
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.86,0:11:24.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為他大概7點下班
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.36,0:11:25.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後我們就…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.86,0:11:32.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊～ 鳴子最後能來太好了～
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.76,0:11:35.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為已經算上鳴子了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.77,0:11:39.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你發短信拒絕我的時候我都不知道怎麼辦好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.11,0:11:41.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是就是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.23,0:11:43.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會惹涼君生氣的呀
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.49,0:11:44.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和涼沒關係！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.62,0:11:46.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.75,0:11:47.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過說真的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.91,0:11:51.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳴子最近都不大和我們來往了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.56,0:11:54.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們還商量過要不要和你絕交呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.95,0:11:57.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的春菜 玩笑過火啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.74,0:11:58.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧 鳴子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.57,0:12:02.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,When we talk about intelligence
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.76,0:12:05.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,we do not mean the ability to get a good score
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.48,0:12:06.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,on a certain kind of test
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.23,0:12:09.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,or even the ability to do well in school
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.70,0:12:11.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,these are at best only…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.51,0:12:25.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 下一班要等30分吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.09,0:12:39.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和平時一樣呢 你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.00,0:12:43.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太過平常了 反倒叫人難受
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.83,0:12:45.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你是希望我怎麼做
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.90,0:12:49.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想讓我罵你「女裝男」嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.64,0:12:52.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.01,0:12:55.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也許那樣我會更感激你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.55,0:12:59.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要隨便拿我尋求心理上的平衡好不好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.13,0:13:03.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多虧了你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.54,0:13:06.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好多時候懸崖勒馬了 謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.30,0:13:15.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…然後就在簡訊裡寫了「喜歡～」
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.54,0:13:18.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現實生活太充實了吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.63,0:13:24.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,專門坐電車 跑到城裡來
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.27,0:13:26.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還拿著那麼大的購物袋
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.07,0:13:28.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是想換衣服吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.41,0:13:29.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和你一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.13,0:13:33.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不靠衣服之類的來改變一下自己
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.25,0:13:34.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會受不了的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.96,0:13:35.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,許多意義上…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.85,0:13:47.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,耶～
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.75,0:13:50.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唱的好～
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.38,0:13:52.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害好厲害好厲害好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.33,0:13:54.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一首 小涼選歌～
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.46,0:13:56.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快選歌啦～
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.56,0:13:58.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂 不要發出那麼淫蕩的聲音啦 JK
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.56,0:13:58.82,explain,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a5}註：選歌那個動詞也有插入的意思…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.85,0:13:59.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.97,0:14:01.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小涼 哪首都可以啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.04,0:14:03.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.76,0:14:04.02,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}哈哈 哪首好呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.05,0:14:06.06,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}春菜 冷靜點…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.18,0:14:04.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玩得高興麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.36,0:14:05.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.77,0:14:07.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺你好像在勉強自己呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.29,0:14:09.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勉強 我沒有…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.13,0:14:13.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說 咱們兩個偷溜吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.93,0:14:15.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.14,0:14:17.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和鳴子要退出咯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.60,0:14:19.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.49,0:14:20.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃 等 等…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.56,0:14:22.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳴子好像身體不太舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.01,0:14:25.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明天也要早起呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.55,0:14:27.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還要看ONE PIECE
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.12,0:14:28.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ONE PIECE是後天播吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.05,0:14:29.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.94,0:14:31.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們太狡猾了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.95,0:14:34.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳴子 之後要好好給我們講講哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.07,0:14:39.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.50,0:14:41.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.07,0:14:45.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.81,0:14:48.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,車站是 這邊？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.18,0:14:55.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 不是一起到車站 這 這樣的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.38,0:14:56.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,討厭啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.22,0:14:59.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偷溜可不是那個意思吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.36,0:15:02.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且我 真的是喝多了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.07,0:15:04.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想稍微休息一下呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.14,0:15:06.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真心的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.78,0:15:09.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我 我是真的身體不舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.45,0:15:11.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以說 休息一下不就好了麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.34,0:15:13.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什 什麼休息一下…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.20,0:15:15.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 對了 ONE PIECE沒關係嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.19,0:15:17.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ONE PIECE不是後天嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.09,0:15:20.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啥！？ 你不是自己說的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.83,0:15:22.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你裝什麼裝啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.89,0:15:24.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.06,0:15:26.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你那裡已經全黑了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.06,0:15:26.41,explain,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a5}註：據說女性[嗶——]多了某處就會變黑
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.08,0:15:28.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.17,0:15:30.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…不要！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.55,0:15:32.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要啦！別碰我…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.33,0:15:33.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啦好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.45,0:15:35.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好你個…頭！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.07,0:15:37.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放開啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.84,0:15:38.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這傢伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.87,0:15:40.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我放手！！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.31,0:15:43.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？ 安城？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.19,0:15:47.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我現在正在和宿海他們玩呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.61,0:15:50.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也來吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.99,0:15:51.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你誰啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.91,0:15:54.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 大家 這邊！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.93,0:15:58.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 什麼啊 耍這種花招
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.37,0:16:14.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,解救被男人纏上的女人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.96,0:16:19.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算是我一生中所做的最普通的事情了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.75,0:16:21.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,解救 就那樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.93,0:16:23.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是應該揍他一頓再拉我走嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.61,0:16:26.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖說我頭腦好 長得又帥
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.53,0:16:28.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惜沒腕力
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.10,0:16:29.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那算啥
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.58,0:16:31.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.40,0:16:33.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還真是 很傻很天真啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.13,0:16:36.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不想被你這麼說呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.88,0:16:37.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這個女裝男
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.78,0:16:42.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對 對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.53,0:16:45.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然 還是被罵來得舒坦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.47,0:16:47.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是處女嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.75,0:16:54.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有 有 有有有什麼問題嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.48,0:16:56.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不要和我交往試試
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.84,0:17:04.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你 你 你你喜歡芽間的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.48,0:17:05.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確實
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.84,0:17:09.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…不行
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.62,0:17:11.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種事是不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.80,0:17:12.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.69,0:17:13.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宿海嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.82,0:17:16.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他那個樣子哪裡好了？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.11,0:17:18.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪裡好…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.62,0:17:19.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要隨便配對啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.78,0:17:21.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰都沒有說喜歡什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.33,0:17:22.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家的領隊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.98,0:17:24.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,頭腦好 運動好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.75,0:17:27.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是以前的事情了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.13,0:17:30.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那倒是 不過…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.15,0:17:32.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他有時候會很體貼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.59,0:17:33.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近也是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.78,0:17:35.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,頭髮好好整理的話
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.63,0:17:38.26,explain,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a5}Hey！Say！JUMP：男性偶像團體
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.63,0:17:38.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也有點兒像Hey！Say！JUMP的山…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.27,0:17:38.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.28,0:17:47.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不知道 到底是不是喜歡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.78,0:17:52.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是 在意宿海而已
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.19,0:17:54.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在意？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.23,0:17:58.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芽間死了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.21,0:18:00.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿姨死了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.09,0:18:02.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟宿海…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.97,0:18:05.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也變得好像很難說上話
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.48,0:18:07.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,進了同一所學校
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.68,0:18:09.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實本來還有些高興的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.09,0:18:10.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.41,0:18:14.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宿海忘不了芽間的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.24,0:18:17.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宿海忘不了芽間…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.32,0:18:19.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你忘不了宿海
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.51,0:18:22.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.58,0:18:27.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才雪集用了宿海的名字吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.49,0:18:28.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說在一起玩
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.84,0:18:40.14,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}特快列車經過 請稍侯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.43,0:18:45.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們 掉隊了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.26,0:19:01.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.76,0:19:08.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咚咚咚 叮！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.76,0:19:08.24,explain,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a5}註：這句話為搞笑藝人原西孝幸名段子的首句 \N也是為死者上香時所敲木魚和小鐘的聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.17,0:19:12.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好吃！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.65,0:19:19.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼你會在我家吃飯啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.84,0:19:22.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是帶山菜了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.87,0:19:24.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然還是天麩羅好吃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.83,0:19:28.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,波波 看上去吃得很香啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.66,0:19:30.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鼻子上面髒了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.82,0:19:34.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 芽間在嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.80,0:19:36.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗨 在的哦～
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.01,0:19:39.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芽間也來吃吧 天麩羅
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.26,0:19:43.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真的相信嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.03,0:19:44.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芽間的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.05,0:19:47.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我之前不是說過了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.72,0:19:48.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.62,0:19:53.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我後來又仔細想過了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.25,0:19:55.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然不是很明白
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.67,0:19:57.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是大概芽間在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.99,0:19:59.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概不是好事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.11,0:20:02.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不能成佛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.15,0:20:06.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才會留在這裡吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.23,0:20:07.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成…佛…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.77,0:20:12.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 我不知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.66,0:20:14.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那種 那種事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.70,0:20:15.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁碳？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.42,0:20:16.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芽間…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.29,0:20:18.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芽間在那裡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.78,0:20:20.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.42,0:20:21.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.08,0:20:22.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈？等…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.03,0:20:24.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 芽間
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.66,0:20:27.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給一點點提示 好不好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.28,0:20:30.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會為你「咚咚咚叮」的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.93,0:20:33.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有願望吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.22,0:20:36.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說 也依靠一下我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.04,0:20:40.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想讓你成佛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.51,0:20:41.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 久川
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.95,0:20:43.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 芽間
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.52,0:20:45.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告訴我吧 拜託
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.39,0:20:48.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…不要只在仁碳面前
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.43,0:20:50.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也在我的面前現個身吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.23,0:20:52.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行嗎？喂！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.00,0:20:53.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那種事…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.04,0:20:57.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芽間也…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.68,0:20:58.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想和大家…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.84,0:21:00.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說話啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.62,0:21:04.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.25,0:21:05.40,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}聽我說 芽間
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.77,0:21:06.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.01,0:21:08.44,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}和大家一起來 好好的想吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.73,0:21:08.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,願望…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.66,0:21:10.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成佛什麼的 這些東西…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.63,0:21:12.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都不懂啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.84,0:21:13.96,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}可以吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.29,0:21:14.89,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.33,0:21:16.37,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}大家一起考慮吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.83,0:21:18.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不懂啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.52,0:21:19.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那樣的話 芽間也…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.65,0:21:20.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,波波！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.62,0:21:28.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要再說了好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.79,0:21:33.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.54,0:21:35.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別再說了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.33,0:21:44.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.06,0:21:54.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不懂啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.69,0:22:55.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒收啦 沒收！！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,//----------------ED-------------------
